data.meta_description: Check out my highlights from my most recent professional season in Finland. Thank you to One Pro Sports Management for giving me the opportunity, and putting…
data.text:
I decided to take a leap of faith and spend one more full season in Finland. Initially the goal was to sign at a first division club, however at this point in my career I wanted to play the most games possible. My first full season in the 2nd division. 10 months away from family and friends is never easy; sacrifices were made, goals were achieved, and growth was gained. Step outside your comfort zone and you’ll be surprised on what you can accomplish. Become comfortable being uncomfortable. Let’s see where this beautiful sport takes me now. ⏳ Thank you football ⚽️

2022 Highlights ▶️ https://lnkd.in/ge8Qp22E [Free Agent - Open to opportunities] Another season comes to an end. Thankful for the opportunity, and the people I met a long the way. The environments I’ve been exposed to truly have a positive impact on my growth not only as an athlete, but as a person as well.
